message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted with excellence. This product boasts a unique blend of quality and functionality that truly sets it apart. Given its exceptional features and craftsmanship, we believe it's worth more than $80. However, I understand everyone has different budgets, so I'm extending this exclusive offer to you at $95. I'm confident you'll find its value far exceeds the investment. Please let me know if you're interested in exploring this opportunity further.
